Closely related to phase mixing is resonant absorption (Ionson 1978). If we assume that some region of plasma has a continuous variation in density or magnetic field, then the Alfvén speed is a continuous quantity and there exists a continuum of Alfvén modes with ωA(x)\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
