				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\omega _D$$\end{document}, that lies within the continuum, then a resonance occurs at locations where ωA(x)=ωD\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
