				\begin{document}$$\vec {v_a}=\vec {B}/\sqrt{\mu _0\rho }$$\end{document}. It can be shown that they can be reduced to the following equation:13∂z→±∂t+(z→∓·∇)z→±=-1ρ∇P-vA→(∇·vA→),\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
